## Node name (override per node)
-name tsss@127.0.0.1

## Cluster cookie
-setcookie tsss_secret_cookie

## SMP
-smp enable
+S 4:4

## Async threads
+A 32

## Max processes
+P 1048576

## Kernel poll
+K true

## Dist buffer (64MB)
+zdbbl 65536

## Manual connection control - kill switch relies on this
-kernel dist_auto_connect never

## Distribution port range
-kernel inet_dist_listen_min 9100
-kernel inet_dist_listen_max 9200
